name: Depa Billaba
Lore: 'Chalactan Jedi Master who was rescued by Mace Windu from space pirates when she was six months old. Jedi Council member who is reknowned for her insights.',
Text: 'Deploys only to Jedi Council Chamber. While at Jedi Council Chamber, immune to attrition and once per turn may use 1 Force to peek at the top card of any Reserve Deck and place that card on top of owner''s Reserve Deck or Used Pile.',
